 />"},{"pid":"254b188e251c408d1c0eef9fd1d0895cc958d109","tid":264783,"uid":110207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T06:52:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>但租車錢一個人分<br />\n住酒店好多時無單人房/同雙人一樣價錢<br />\n食野嗌唔到多幾樣試</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n結果朋友只係用黎分擔錢銀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個人就唔住酒店啦，住青宿算了。<br />\n最尾個樣就真係駁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果你唔介意錢銀<br />\n一條友真係好啲<br />\n呀仲有渣機影相"},{"pid":"0f63ed8e84c9c0fee5c11ce96ae0f5c9d623fa92","tid":264783,"uid":120157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T06:58:07.000Z","msg":"各有各好處<br />\n如果同朋友去，不如買機票前同對方傾下自己去旅行想點<br />\n好過去完旅行就少個朋友<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9779ff4a5181f6c781815b14cad7de2de74e1e4b","tid":264783,"uid":34692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T10:03:15.000Z","msg":"我覺得只係你冇遇到啲好嘅旅伴<br />\n上年我同個fd 去咗兩星期旅行，雖然行程係我plan 功課都係我做， 不過佢真係去邊都冇所謂又冇抱怨， 係咁嘅情況之下我覺得兩個人去好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"739e7371c1f382382fb224d7934678cb1abec4ee","tid":264783,"uid":69761,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T10:03:59.000Z","msg":"跳樓啦"},{"pid":"06daa47176309c6efee1fc9d76b5c2361d91f870","tid":264783,"uid":65931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T11:57:10.000Z","msg":"3果點真係好認同 !"},{"pid":"37ddd4f3cd767413bddef1571899f5a782a650ec","tid":264783,"uid":93266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T11:59:52.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"c5fdbc0b59fd47247895fce1537d58561c79aa14","tid":264783,"uid":34181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T12:33:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得只係你冇遇到啲好嘅旅伴<br />\n上年我同個fd 去咗兩星期旅行，雖然行程係我plan 功課都係我做， 不過佢真係去邊都冇所謂又冇抱怨， 係咁嘅情況之下我覺得兩個人去好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自問我唔介意Plan野，<br />\n係個人既態度令我煩躁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大佬咁Hea既你不如係屋企摺/去旅行團算啦，<br />\n冇租車既情況下預早少少搭車是常識吧。<br />\n你估度度都好似香港咁方便，<br />\n三個字內有車，一個鐘頭內到埗咩。<br />\n<br />\n所以我再重申一次，<br />\n要Hea冇問題，<br />\n自已慢慢Hea啦。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27051e3f76ecbc222112748b4f768b6cace6c367","tid":264783,"uid":34181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T12:34:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>各有各好處<br />\n如果同朋友去，不如買機票前同對方傾下自己去旅行想點<br />\n好過去完旅行就少個朋友<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔會冇朋友既，<br />\n係下次知路，唔會再同佢去咁囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d634ef6bd188edc1f37f679d34ee4a1a00d90aab","tid":264783,"uid":34181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T15:21:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"530880353f45e76060d641614dfa7acc04c4e9ba","tid":264783,"uid":111934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T15:25:10.000Z","msg":"朋友肯唔肯入鄉隨俗又係一個問題<br />\n試過同唔太熟嘅朋友去日本<br />\n食完嘢例牌扮傻唔收拾餐盤就走<br />\n搭JR 就大聲吹水<br />\n全程超級痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b301e1b2dd68819c3c39bee85c080fd3024166a3","tid":264783,"uid":34181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T16:06:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>朋友肯唔肯入鄉隨俗又係一個問題<br />\n試過同唔太熟嘅朋友去日本<br />\n食完嘢例牌扮傻唔收拾餐盤就走<br />\n搭JR 就大聲吹水<br />\n全程超級痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n嘩超級尷尬<br />\n係咪好想扮唔識佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過有冇提下佢地先<br />\n佢地可能唔知呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b19e9d843660d17cb0744ef3efc7936f15ba46b2","tid":264783,"uid":34181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T00:47:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2bb5398f04682a9722610a60bc0b102d2a39ba1","tid":264783,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T03:09:33.000Z","msg":"同朋友去幾個人陪住安全感大啲既<br />\n不過上次同朋友去唔係咁開心<br />\n黎緊6月尾毒遊"},{"pid":"5d3c6b461a05f0d92651dc7d1cfe75ba4d911342","tid":264783,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T03:10:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得只係你冇遇到啲好嘅旅伴<br />\n上年我同個fd 去咗兩星期旅行，雖然行程係我plan 功課都係我做， 不過佢真係去邊都冇所謂又冇抱怨， 係咁嘅情況之下我覺得兩個人去好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nGood fd 巴打要珍惜"},{"pid":"b609b6b611851df4828d00ada2a2fd0e8e63cbc3","tid":264783,"uid":42586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T03:43:59.000Z","msg":"仲有:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 勁大聲講嘢 搞到全部人望住哂<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 對當地人冇禮貌<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去到當地呢樣又話唔食個樣又話污漕<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Plan好哂去個啲地方出發前唔睇<br />\n     到咗先話唔想去"},{"pid":"8e45aea41322f89d59fbde5cc3d214079fc0304d","tid":264783,"uid":34181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T07:05:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 勁大聲講嘢 搞到全部人望住哂<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 對當地人冇禮貌<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去到當地呢樣又話唔食個樣又話污漕<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Plan好哂去個啲地方出發前唔睇<br />\n     到咗先話唔想去</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n搭左幾個鐘頭車先話嫌悶要走，<br />\n問佢可以去邊又唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2275acee92983d3cc0c87ac4dec377be8a7c12ee","tid":264783,"uid":34181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T07:08:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同朋友去幾個人陪住安全感大啲既<br />\n不過上次同朋友去唔係咁開心<br />\n黎緊6月尾毒遊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去邊毒遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30ab2718a2fbb4a4bd0ef4999f291b0e767e4e16","tid":264783,"uid":49344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T07:11:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>但租車錢一個人分<br />\n住酒店好多時無單人房/同雙人一樣價錢<br />\n食野嗌唔到多幾樣試</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n結果朋友只係用黎分擔錢銀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個人就唔住酒店啦，住青宿算了。<br />\n最尾個樣就真係駁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有錢一樣可以嗌好多樣野食<br />\n結論：旅伴只係用黎夾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2894aeef776b3adc7831d6705de1cd6995c1b22","tid":264783,"uid":34181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T08:27:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>但租車錢一個人分<br />\n住酒店好多時無單人房/同雙人一樣價錢<br />\n食野嗌唔到多幾樣試</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n結果朋友只係用黎分擔錢銀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個人就唔住酒店啦，住青宿算了。<br />\n最尾個樣就真係駁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有錢一樣可以嗌好多樣野食<br />\n結論：旅伴只係用黎夾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有錢我仲唔包條女陪我去旅行？"}]}